idCitation.resTitle: East Asia, Southeast Asia, Alaska 1:2,000,000 Maps Index

dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer provides an index map that can be used to locate individual scanned map sheets.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon shapefile is an index to 1:2,000,000 scale maps of East Asia, Southeast Asia, Alaska, titled '二百万分一大東亜航空圖 - Nihyakumanbunnoichi Daitōa Kōkūzu.’ To create this index, footprints were generated using the fishnet tool, and metadata were supplied for the digitized paper maps by Stanford University Libraries. After the footprints were created, the shapefile was trimmed and labeled according to the sources.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Stanford University Libraries, Stanford Geospatial Center
